quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Araninahajwe uwufise muminwe yiwe ubwami bwose, kandi niwe nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  67,2,"Niwe yaremye urupfu hamwe n’ubuzima kugira ngo ibagerageze imenye uwariwe muri mwebwe afise ibikorwa vyiza gusumba, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ikigongwe"
  67,3,"Niwe yaremye Amajuru yose uko ari indwi agerekeranye kuyandi, mbega ntubona itandukaniro iryariryo ryose mukurema kwa nyene imigisha, rero n’uhindukize amaso yawe ugume uvuga uti:- mbega urabona mwo ikosa"
  67,4,"Kandi garura amaso yawe kenshi na kenshi, hanyuma iryo jisho ryawe rizo garuka riteterewe nawe warushe"
  67,5,"Mu vy’ukuri twarasharije iri Juru riri hafi n’amatara, kandi twagize gutyo kugira ngo dukubite amashetani, kandi twabashiriye ho ibihano biteguye vy’umuriro waka n’inguvu nyinshi cane"
  67,6,"N’abahakanye Umuremyi wabo w’ukuri, hariho ibihano vy’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu n’ingaruka mbi imeze gute"
  67,7,Ni batabwa muriwo bazo kwumva isumo ryawo n’ingene umoka
  67,8,"Uregereje gusaduka kubera ishavu ryawo no hejuru y’abantu babi, uko hatawe mwo umurwi w’abantu babi, aba wucungereye nabo bazoba baza bati :- mbega ntimwashikiwe n’uwutuza"
  67,9,"Nabo bazo kwishura bati:- mbega ni kuki twashikiwe n’uwutuza? Mugabo twebwe twarahakanye n’ukuvuga duti:- Imana nta nakimwe yamanuye, namwe ntaho muri atari mubuzimire buniniya cane"
  67,10,"Bazovuga bati :- iyo tuba twumva canke iyo tuba dufise ubwenge ntitwari kuba abantu bo mumuriro udahera"
  67,11,"Baremeza ibicumuro vyabo, rero uguhonywa kwabo kuraba kwiye abo bantu bo mu muriro udahera"
  67,12,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batinya Umuremyi wabo nabo batamubona bazoronka imbabazi n’impembo niniya cane
  67,13,"Nimugire amabanga y’imvugo zanyu canke muziserure, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  67,14,Ntamenye uwaremye nayo ariyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibitazwi hamwe n’ibizwi
  67,15,"Niyo yagize Isi ngo ishobore gukora kubera mwebwe, rero ni mugenzure kumpande zayo zose, kandi mufungure kumigisha yayo, no kuriyo niho twese tuzo subirayo"
  67,16,"Mbega mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iyo mw’ijuru itazoba cinyiriza kw’Isi, mukaza mubona Isi iranyiganze"
  67,17,"Canke mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iri mw’ijuru ubwami bwiwe ni buniniya yuko itazoba zanira igihuhusi kivanzwe mwo umusenyi n’amabuye, niho muzomenya ituza ryanje"
  67,18,"Ntankeka barahakanye abariho imbere yabo, mbega kwabaye gute ugushavura kwanje"
  67,19,"Mbega ntibabona inyoni ziri hejuru yabo ingene zigorora amababa yazo n’ukuyazinga, nta n’umwe azi zitirira atari Imana nyene imigisha myinshi, mu vy’ukuri niyo ibona ibintu vyose"
  67,20,Canke n’izihe ngabo zanyu zishobora kuba kingira atari nyene imigisha myinshi? Ntaba hakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri atari uguhendwa gusa
  67,21,Canke ni nde azobaha imigisha mugihe ibazitiriye iyo migisha yayo ahubwo babandanya mu bwiyonkore bwabo n’urwankano gusa
  67,22,"Mbega uwugenda ajunjamitse umutwe wiwe atamerewe neza, mbega niwe mweranda, canke uwugenda atumbereye inzira igororotse"
  67,23,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabaremye n’ukubaha amatwi n’amaso hamwe n’imitima, rero nibakeyi cane bashima iyo ngabirano yanyu"
  67,24,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabatandukanije kw’Isi, niwe niho muzo kwegeranywa"
  67,25,"Nabo bavuga bati:- niryari iryo sango nimwaba mu vugisha ukuri"
  67,26,"Vuga uti :- ubumenyi bwavyo buri ku Mana, kandi mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi umutuza gusa n’uwuba sobanurira"
  67,27,"Mugabo mugihe bazo kibonera kiri hafi, amaso y’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri azo mara mara hanyuma havurwe hati:- ibi nivyo mwahora musaba"
  67,28,"Vuga uti:- ni mumbwire yuko Imana niya mponya jewe, hamwe nabo turi kumwe, canke itugiriye impuhwe zayo, none ni nde azoba kingira abo bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ibihano vy’Imana bibabaza"
  67,29,"Vuga uti:- Imana niyo nyene impuhwe nyinshi twebwe tuyemera n’ukuyizera, nubu vuba muzo menya uwuri m’ubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  67,30,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe mubona gute nkiyo amazi yanyu yoba yibijwe mu kuzimu, none ni nde yobazanira amazi meza y’isoko"
  68,1,"Nuun, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa). Kandi ndarahiye kw’ikaramu hamwe nivyo bandikisha ko"
  68,2,"No kumigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, wewe nturi umusazi"
  68,3,Mu vy’ukuri wewe urafise impembo idahera
  68,4,Kandi ntankeka wewe urafise ingeso nziza cane
  68,5,"Rero ubu vuba uzo bona, nabo nyene bazobona"
  68,6,Ni nde afise ibisazi muri mwebwe
  68,7,"Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’uwazimiye munzira yiwe, kandi irabazi cane abarongotse"
  68,8,Rero ntuba gamburukire abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri
  68,9,Bagomba yuko wo borohereza nabo bakorohererwa
  68,10,Kandi ntugamburukire uwurahira cane nawe ari mu bantu batishoboye
  68,11,Umuvuzi w’insaku agenda asasagaza urwanko mu bantu
  68,12,"Akingira imigisha nugu hemukira ibiremwa nkawe, n’uguhakana Imana yiwe"
  68,13,"Nyene\tumutima\tukomeye,\tkuri\tivyo\tvyose\tni\tnk’ikintu\tcashinguwe ahantu mugabo ntigishingurwe neza"
  68,14,Kubera yuko afise amatungo n’ibibondo
  68,15,"Mugihe\tasomewe\tamajambo\tyacu\tmatagtifu\tavuga\tati:-\taya\tniya majambo y’ububeshi bw’abantu ba kera"
  68,16,Tuzo mushira ko inkovu kw’izuru ryiwe
  68,17,"Mu vy’ukuri abo bantu tuzobaha ibibazo nkuko twashize ko ibibazo kubari bafise imirima, mugihe barahira yuko bazo kwimbura kuri iyo mirima nihashika mu gitondo"
  68,18,Kandi ntibabwiye n’umukene numwe
  68,19,Rero warashikiwe n’ivyago bivuye ku Muremyi wabo nabo basinziriye
  68,20,Uwo murima uba nk’uwahiye
  68,21,Bukeye bara hamagarana
  68,22,"Yuko\tbogenda\thakiri\tkare\tku\tmurima\twanyu\tnimwaba\tmushaka kwimbura"
  68,23,Baragiye bongorerana
  68,24,Yuko uno musi ata mukene yinjira
  68,25,"Baragenda mugitondo biyumvira yuko bafise ububasha\tbw’ukuba buza ba bakene"
  68,26,"Mugihe\tbabona\twa\tmurima\tbaciye\tbavuga\tbati:-\tntankeka\ttwebwe twazimiye"
  68,27,Canke batwankiye
  68,28,"Umwe mubagira neza yavuze ati:- mbega sinaba bwiye yuko mu garuka ku Muremyi wanyu mu musabe ikigongwe"
  68,29,"Nabo ba mwishura bati:- iteka ni ry’Umuremyi wacu, mu vy’ukuri twara hemukiye imitima yacu"
  68,30,Baca bahangana n’abandi baterana imyikomo
  68,31,"Bavuga\tbati:-\turu\tn’uruhombo\trwacu,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\ttwari\ttwararenze imbibe z’Imana"
  68,32,"Nkumbure\tUmuremyi\twacu\tazo\tduhindurira\tuwundi\tmurima\tmwiza gusumba uwu, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turiyegereje ku Muremyi wacu"
  68,33,"Uku\tniko\tbiba\tibihano\tvy’Umuremyi\twawe,\tn’ibihano\tvy’umusi w’imperuka ni bininiya cane gusumba nkiyo bobi menya"
  68,34,"Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazoba bafise ijuru rifise imigisha y’Umuremyi wabo"
  68,35,Mbega tubagire abagamburutsi nk’abononyi
  68,36,"Mbega mubaye gute, muca intahe gute"
  68,37,Canke murafise igitabu musomamwo
  68,38,Yuko muzoronka ivyo mwipfuza
  68,39,Canke murafise amasezerano kuri twebwe azoguma ho kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka yuko muzoronka ivyo mwiganzira
  68,40,"N’ubabaze muti :- ni nde muribo yofata ingwati kuri ibi vyose"
  68,41,"Canke barafise abo bacuditse hamwe, rero nibabazane abo bacuditse hamwe niba bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  68,42,"Kuri uwo musi hazoba ibihano bikaze cane, bazo hamagarwa gupfukama bashira imitwe yabo hasi, mugabo ntibazo shobora"
  68,43,"Amaso yabo azoba araba hasi, agahinda nako kabapfuke, mu vy’ukuri bahora bahamagarwa gupfukama bashire imitwe yabo hasi mugihe bari mubantu beranda"
  68,44,"Nundeke hamwe n’abahakana ibi biganiro, tuzoba kwega buhoro buhoro mubihano vyacu ku hantu batazi"
  68,45,"Ndabahaye umwanya, mu vy’ukuri ububasha bwanje bura komeye cane"
  68,46,Canke urabasaba impembo nabo bakarengerwa nayo magarama
  68,47,Canke kuribo hariho ubumenyi bw’amabanga bahawe bw’intumwa z’Imana bandika
  68,48,"Rero n’utenyenye kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntube nk’uwamizwe n’ifi, mugihe yatabaza Imana yiwe nawe ageramiwe nabi cane"
  68,49,"Iyo adashikirwa n’imigisha ivuye ku Muremyi wiwe, ntankeka yari gutabwa ku nkengera y’ikiyaga nawe atabwa ko umwikomo"
  68,50,Mugabo Umuremyi wiwe niwe yamugenye nukumugira mu bantu b’intungane
  68,51,"Nayo ba bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, baregereza kuguhuvya n’amaso yabo, mugihe bumvise ubutumwa bwawe nuguca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri uyu muntu n’umusazi"
  68,52,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ari icibutso kubantu bose
  69,1,Icabaye c’ukuri
  69,2,Nico cabaye c’ukuri n’igiki
  69,3,N’igiki kizo kumenyesha ico kintu cabaye c’ukuri
  69,4,Bene Thamudu na bene Aadi barahakanye umusi w’umuhero w’isi
  69,5,Rero abo bene Thamudu barahonejwe kuvyago bininiya cane
  69,6,Nayo bene Aadi barahonejwe n’igihuhusi gikaze cane kida kingirwa
  69,7,"Wabatwaye amajoro indwi n’imitaga umunani, ubwo nyene uda hengeshanije, ugasanga abantu baguye igihumure nkakumwe kw’ibishitsi vy’imitende vyaguye hasi bimeze nk’imiroha"
  69,8,Mbega wabonye umwe muribo yasigaye
  69,9,"Na Fir’auni hamwe n’abamyeho imbere yiwe nabo mubisagara vyahinduwe, nabone baragize amakosa"
  69,10,Bariyonkora kuntumwa z’Umuremyi wabo ari naho yabafata kunguvu zitabaho
  69,11,"Mugihe umwuzurire w’amazi washika, twebwe twarabadugije tuburiza muri ico kigenda aribwo bwato"
  69,12,"Kugira ngo kibe icibutso kuri mwebwe, n’ugutwi kwumva kwumvire ho"
  69,13,N’igihe hazovuzwa inzamba izovuzwa rimwe gusa
  69,14,N’Isi hamwe n’Imisozi bizo kurwaho n’ugusenyurwa rimwe gusa
  69,15,Kuri uwo musi ibizoba bizoba vyamaze kuba
  69,16,"N’amajuru\tazo\tmanyagurika,\trero\tkuri\tuwo\tmusi\tAmajuru\tazoba ahoyahoya cane"
  69,17,"N’Abamarayika\tbazoba\tbari\thambavu\tyayo\tmajuru\tn’Abamarayika b’ubwoko umunani nibo bazorerura inyegamo y’iteka y’Umuremyi wawe"
  69,18,Kuri uwo musi mwese muzo kwerekwa naho hatazo nyegezwa amabanga yanyu yose
  69,19,"Rero\tuwuzo\thabwa\tigitabu\tc’ibikorwa\tvyiwe\tmu\tkuboko\tkwiwe kw’iburyo azovuga n’akamwemwe kenshi ati:- ni musome igitabu canje"
  69,20,Mu vy’ukuri ndazi yuko nzohabwa ibiharuro vyanje
  69,21,Nawe azoba ari mu buzima bw’akanyamuneza ntangere
  69,22,Mw’ijuru ritagatifu
  69,23,Ivyamwa bigerekeranye kubindi bizoba hafi kuribo
  69,24,"Nimufungure muteko munywe n’umunezero ntangere, kubera ibikorwa mwagize muri iyo misi yahera"
  69,25,"Mugabo\tuwuzohabwa\tigitabu\tciwe\tmukuboko\tkwiwe\tkw’ibubamfu azovuga ati :- Yo! Iyo ntohawe iki gitabu canje"
  69,26,Kandi sinari kumenya ikihe giharuro canje
  69,27,Iyo urupfu rumarira ivyanje vyose
  69,28,Amatungo yanje ntaco yamariye
  69,29,Ubutegetsi bwanje bwara ntakaranye
  69,30,Ni mumufate mumushire ko iminyororo
  69,31,Hanyuma mumujugunyire mumuriro udahera
  69,32,Kandi abe yaboshwe n’umunyororo ufise uburebure bw’imetero mirongo indwi muce mu mwinjiza yo
  69,33,Mu vy’ukuri ntiyigeze yemera Imana yiwe ntagatifu
  69,34,Kandi ntiya himiriza abandi kugira ngo arishe abakene
  69,35,Rero uno musi ngaha ntamukunzi muhire n’umwe afise
  69,36,Nta n’ibifungurwa afise atari amazi y’amashira gusa
  69,37,Ntiba gufungura ivyo bifungurwa atari abanya vyaha
  69,38,Rero ndarahiye kubintu mubona
  69,39,N’ivyo mutabona
  69,40,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taka\tn’akamo\tkazanywe\tn’intumwa\ty’Imana\tifise\titeka rininiya cane"
  69,41,"Kandi s’imvugo y’umwanditsi w’amajambo y’ubuhizi nkuko mu bivuga, nani bakeyi cane muyemera"
  69,42,"Kandi\ts’amajambo\ty’umurozi\tnkuko\tmubivuga,\tni\tgakeyi\tcane\tkuri mwebwe kugira ngo mushobore kwemera ubu butumwa"
  69,43,N’imanurwa rivuye ku Muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  69,44,Iyo yiyadukiza kuri twebwe bimwe mu majambo asanzwe gusa
  69,45,Ntankeka twebwe twari kumu cakira n’ukuboko kw’iburyo
  69,46,Kandi mu vy’ukuri twari kumuca umutsi mukuru w’umutima wiwe
  69,47,Kandi nta n’umwe muri mwebwe yari kutubuza mukuta mufata
  69,48,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu n’ubutumwa ku bantu bagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri
  69,49,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\tturazi\tneza\tyuko\tmuri\tmwebwe\tharimwo abahakanyi"
  69,50,Uzoba ari umubabaro ku bantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  69,51,Mu vy’ukuri uku n’ukuri nyakuri
  69,52,"Rero n’uninahaze izina ry’Umuremyi wawe ariwe mukuru. Igisomwa c’Ukuduga.\tIkigabane\tca (29). Camanukiye IMakkat. Gifise imirongo"
  70,1,Uwabajije abaza kubijanye n’ibihano bizoba
  70,2,Kubera abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bada shobora kuwu hagarika uwo musi
  70,3,Bivuye ku Mana nyene iteka rikuru cane
  70,4,Abamarayika hamwe n’imitima y’abantu bose yama iduga iwe k’umusi waho ikiringo cayo ari imyaka ibihumbi mirongo itanu
  70,5,Rero ni wigumye kuwigumya neza
  70,6,Mu vy’ukuri uwo musi w’umuhero w’isi bo bawubona yuko uri kure cane
  70,7,Natwe tuwubona yuko uri hafi cane
  70,8,Umusi amajuru azoba nk’ubutare bw’umujumpu bwashaye cane
  70,9,N’Imisozi ikazoba nk’isufi zaguruwe ziri mukirere
  70,10,N’umugenzi ntazo baza mugenzi wiwe
  70,11,Naho bogirwa ngo babonane nuwuri mumakosa azokwipfuza yuko yo kwikombora n’ibihano vy’uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi mu gutanga ibibondo vyiwe
  70,12,N’umukenyezi wiwe hamwe na bene wabo
  70,13,N’abagenzi biwe bamukikuje kumpande zose
  70,14,N’ibiri kw’isi vyose hanyuma arokoke
  70,15,"Mugabo sivyo, mu vy’ukuri uwo n’umuriro waka neza cane"
  70,16,Ubabura urukoba rw’umubiri rimwe na rimwe
  70,17,"Uzo\thamagara\tkuwahindukije\tumugongo\twiwe\tnuguhindukira\tmu kutitaho inyigisho z’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani"
  70,18,N’uwegeranije amatungo yiwe hanyuma akayaziganya
  70,19,Mu vy’ukuri umuntu yaremwe n’igihababu cinshi
  70,20,Mugihe ashikiwe n’ishari niho aca asimbwa n’umutima
  70,21,Ashikiwe n’amahirwe aca yigungira ko
  70,22,Dukuye mwo abasenga Imana yabo y’ukuri
  70,23,N’abatsimbataza amasengesho yabo
  70,24,N’abafise mu matungo yabo harimwo igice cabo kizwi neza
  70,25,Kubera uwasavye n’uwigumya mu kudasega
  70,26,N’abemera umusi w’impembo
  70,27,N’abatinya ibihano vy’Umuremyi wabo
  70,28,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vy’Umuremyi wabo si ivyu kurokoka kw’umuntu w’umunyavyaha
  70,29,N’abapfuka ibitsina vyabo
  70,30,"Dukuye mwo abakenyezi babo canke bamwe batunzwe bari mu minwe yabo y’iburyo, abo nibo badatabwako umwikomo"
  70,31,"Mugabo abipfuza kuronka ibitari ibi, abo nibo barenga imbibe zagenywe n’Imana"
  70,32,Naba ziganya ivyabo hamwe n’amasezerano yabo
  70,33,Naba hagaze neza mukuba ivyabona vyabo
  70,34,Naba bunga bunga amasengesho yabo
  70,35,Abo nibo bazoba bari mu mirima bafise urupfasoni ntangere
  70,36,Bafise iki bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri mugihe bagukanuriye amaso yabo gusa
  70,37,Imirwi y’abantu n’iyindi izoba iri k’uruhande rw’iburyo n’ibubamfu
  70,38,Mbega umwe wese muribo yizeye yuko azo kwinjizwa muri iryo juru ry’imigisha
  70,39,"Oya! Sivyo, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twabaremye muvyo bazi"
  70,40,Rero ndarahiye ku Muremyi wo m’ubuseruko bwose no mu burengero bwose yuko twebwe tubishoboye
  70,41,"Kubahindura abari intungane gusumba abahahora, natwe ntitunaniwe"
  70,42,"Rero\tnimubareke\tbiyagire\tayamuhe\tbateko\tbafyinate,\tkugeza\tnaho bazobona umusi wabo bemerewe"
  70,43,Umusi bazova mu ntatemwa zabo ningoga na ningoga nkuko birukira aho basiganirwa ho
  70,44,"Amaso yabo azoba yunamye apfutswe n’ibimaramare, uwo niwo musi bahora bemererwa"
  71,1,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) ku bantu biwe, yuko yobatuza imbere yuko bashikirwa n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  71,2,"Nawe\tavuga\tati:-\temwe\tbantu\tbanje,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tndi\tuwutuza mboneka neza kuri mwebwe"
  71,3,"Yuko mwosenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri, muyigamburukire kandi munyubahe"
  71,4,"Izoba girira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyanyu, kandi izoba tebereza kugeza k’umwanya wagenewe, mu vy’ukuri naho impanuka yoturuka ku Mana ntikingirwa nk’iyo mwobimenya"
  71,5,"Intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yavuze iti:- ewe Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri abantu banje jewe nabashikirije ubutumwa ijoro n’umutaga"
  71,6,Mugabo ubutumwa bwanje nta nakimwe bwongereje atari uku mpunga gusa
  71,7,"Nuko naba hamagara kugira ngo ubagirire ikigongwe, baca baziba amatwi yabo bakoresheje intoke zabo, n’ukwipfuka impuzu zabo hose, baca bongereza babandanya guhakana n’ukwishima kwinshi cane"
  71,8,Kandi jewe naraba hamagaye k’umugaragaro
  71,9,"Hanyuma ndabatera akamo k’ijwi rirerire, kandi ndavugana nabo mu mwiherero"
  71,10,"Ndababwira nti:- ni musabe ikigongwe ku Muremyi wanyu, mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi gusumba"
  71,11,Izoba zanira ibicu bisesa gurika imvura nyinshi cane
  71,12,"Kandi izobaha amatungo hamwe n’ibibondo, kandi izobaha n’imirima, kandi ibagirire n’inzuzi"
  71,13,"Mubaye gute, nta rupfasoni mugirira Imana"
  71,14,Mugihe ariyo yabaremye muri ubu buryo n’ubundi
  71,15,"Mbega\tnti\tmubona\tingene\tImana\tyaremye\tAmajuru\tuko\tari\tindwi agerekeranye kuyandi"
  71,16,"N’ukugira Ukwezi muri kwo kube ari umuco, n’ukugira Izuba kuba ari itara"
  71,17,N’Imana yaraba nagishije kw’isi ibiterwa
  71,18,Hanyuma izoba subiza muri yo kandi izo bakuramwo
  71,19,N’Imana yarabagiriye Isi kuba ikintu ciza mwasasiwe
  71,20,Kugira ngo mugire kuriyo mu nzira z’agutse
  71,21,"Intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yavuze iti:- Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri abo bantu banje biyonkoye kuri jewe, kandi bakurikiye abafise amatungo yabo n’ibibondo vyabo ata kindi babongereje atari uruhombo gusa"
  71,22,Baca bagira ingeso niniya z’uguta idini
  71,23,"N’abababwiye aba bakurikiye bati:- ntimusige Imana zanyu canke ntimusige uwitwa Waddan hamwe na Suwa’a, na Yaghutha na Yauqa na Nas’raa"
  71,24,"Nabo bakaba baratakaje abantu benshi, rero ntubongereze aba hemukiye imitima y’abo atari ukuzimirira kure"
  71,25,"Rero kubera amakosa yabo baciye bibizwa mumazi n’ukwinjizwa mu muriro udahera, kandi ntiba ronse ababa tabara imbere y’Imana"
  71,26,"N’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yagumye abandanya avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntusige uwariwe wese kuri iy’Isi muri abo bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  71,27,"Mu vy’ukuri niwaba siga abo bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazo zimiza abantu bawe barongotse, kandi ntibazo kwibaruka atari ibibondo bibi cane vy’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri nkuko kwabo"
  71,28,"Muremyi wanje, jewe n’ungirire ikigongwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banje, hamwe n’uwinjiye munzu yanje nawe ari umu Isilamu, hamwe naba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe naba Isilamu kazi, kandi ntu bongereze abahemukiye imitima yabo atari ukuba honya gusa"
  72,1,"Vuga uti:- naramenyeshejwe kuri jewe yuko umurwi umwe w’ibisigo wumvise amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani uca uvuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri twumvise amajambo ya Qur’ani y’igitangaza"
  72,2,"Irongora k’uburongozi, kuri ivyo natwe turayemeye kandi ntituzo kwigera tugereranya Imana n’ikindi kintu hamwe n’Umuremyi wacu"
  72,3,Kandi mu vy’ukuri iteka ry’Umuremyi wacu riratewe iteka rihagije cane kuko itigeze yigirira umukenyezi canke ikibondo
  72,4,Mu vy’ukuri abadafise ubwenge muri twebwe bamye bavuga amajambo yarengeje urugero hejuru y’Imana
  72,5,Natwe twamye twiyumvira yuko abantu hamwe n’ibisigo batazo besha hejuru y’Imana
  72,6,"Mu vy’ukuri hari abagabo mubiremwa vy’Imana bikingira kubagabo b’ibisigo, kuri ivyo babongereza ingorane zidasanzwe"
  72,7,Mu vy’ukuri biketse nkuko mwiketse mwebwe yuko Imana itazo zana iyindi ntumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose
  72,8,Natwe twarakoze kumajuru tuyabona acungerewe n’abafise inguvu hamwe n’inyenyeri zisa yangana
  72,9,Mu vy’ukuri twahora twicara mu nyubakwa kugira ngo twumvirize mugabo uwashaka kwumviriza ubwo nyene yahasanga ibishirira vy’umucanwa bimu rorereye
  72,10,"Natwe ntavyo twari tuzi yuko bashakirwa ishari bamwe baba ngaha kw’isi, canke Umuremyi wabo abashakira uburokoke"
  72,11,"Mu vy’ukuri muri twebwe harimwo abantu beza n’abandi muri twebwe bateye ukundi, rero turi mu nzira zitandukanye"
  72,12,Natwe twari tuzi yuko tudashobora gutsinda Imana kuri iy’Isi kandi tudashobora kumwiyaka ngo twiruke
  72,13,Natwe mugihe twumva ubwo burokoke twaciye tubwemera rero uwemeye Umuremyi wiwe ntazotinya kuzimbwa canke kwegekwako ibicumuro vy’uwundi muntu
  72,14,Natwe harimwo bamwe muri twebwe bemeye kuba aba Isilamu hakaba n’abandi muri twebwe baguma bajuragirika bamaze kuba aba Isilamu abo nibo barondeye uburokoke
  72,15,N’abajuragirika abo bazoba ari inkwi zo mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  72,16,Iyo bafata nka nkama inzira igororotse twari kuba nywesha amazi menshi
  72,17,"Kugira\tngo\ttubagerageze\tkuri\tivyo\tvyose\tn’uwutitaho\tmu\tkwibuka Umuremyi wiwe, izomu sunika mubihano bigoye cane"
  72,18,"Mu vy’ukuri amasengero yose nay’Imana, rero ntimusenge uwariwe wese hamwe n’Imana y’ukuri"
  72,19,Mu vy’ukuri umushumvyi w’Imana Muhammadi (aui) igihe yahagarara asaba Umuremyi wiwe bari hafi yukumurwako
  72,20,"Vuga uti:- Jewe nsenga Umuremyi wanje gusa, kandi sinda mugereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  72,21,"Vuga\tuti:-\tjewe\tsindabaganza\tkugira\tngo\tndabagirire\tinabi,\tcanke kubarongora"
  72,22,"Vuga\tuti:-\tntankeka\tntan’umwe\tashobora\tkunkingira\tn’Imana,\tkandi sinzoronka ibwicaro bw’amahoro atari kuriyo yonyene gusa"
  72,23,"Mugabo mugushikiriza ubutumwa buvuye ku Mana hamwe n’amategeko yayo, hamwe n’abazokwiyonjorora ku Mana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo ntankeka bazoronswa umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bazowubamwo mu buzima bwabo bwose"
  72,24,"Kugeza aho bazobonera ivyo bemerewe, niho bazotahura uwariwe afise umufasha uhoya hoya n’uwufise igitigiri gitoyi"
  72,25,"Vuga uti:- sindabizi yuko ivyo mwemerewe biri hafi canke Umuremyi wanje azo biha ikiringo kirekire"
  72,26,"Niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’amabanga yose, kandi ntiyereka uwariwe wese amabanga yayo"
  72,27,"Dukuye mwo intumwa yayo yemereye, uyo niyo yashiriye ho abamu kingira bari imbere yiwe n’inyuma yiwe"
  72,28,"Kugira ngo atahure yuko bashikanye ubutumwa bw’umuremyi wabo, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo bafise vyose, kandi niyo yafashe nka nkama igitigiri c’ibintu vyose"
  73,1,Wewe wipfutse amahuzu
  73,2,Nuhagarare mw’ijoro mugabo mu mwanya mutoyi gusa
  73,3,Igice c’iryo joro canke ugabanye gatoyi
  73,4,"Canke wongerezeko gatoyi, hanyuma usome iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu nkuko bitegetswe"
  73,5,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzo kumanurira imvugo iremereye cane
  73,6,Mu vy’ukuri ukwikangura mw’ijoro n’ukugira ibisabisho bihurana neza n’umushaha hamwe n’amajambo yayo ahumuriza cane
  73,7,Mu vy’ukuri k’umurango urafise ibikorwa vyinshi cane
  73,8,Nurivuge izina ry’Umuremyi wawe kandi witeho kuriyo bimwe vy’ukuri
  73,9,"Umuremyi\tw’ubuseruko\tnuburengera\tzuba,\tntayindi\tisengwa\tatariyo yonyene gusa, rero n’uyigire kuba ariyo igukingiye"
  73,10,"Ni\twigumye kuri ivyo vyose bavuga abo bahakanyi b’Imana,\tkandi ubikure ko ube kure yabo n’amahoro"
  73,11,"N’undeke\tjewe\thamwe\tnabo\tbahakanyi\tbaronse\tamahirwe,\thanyuma ubahe ikiringo kigufiya gusa"
  73,12,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turafise ibihano hamwe n’umuriro udahera waka cane
  73,13,N’ibifungurwa biniga mu muhogo hamwe n’ibihano bibabaza cane
  73,14,"K’umusi\twaho\tIsi\thamwe\tn’Imisozi\tizo\tnyiganzwa,\tn’Imisozi\tikazoba nk’iyegeranijwe nk’umusenyi udafadika"
  73,15,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba zaniye intumwa y’Imana y’icabona kuri mwebwe, nkuko twamutwariye intumwa y’Imana kwa Fir’auni"
  73,16,"Mugabo Fir’auni yariyonkoye kuntumwa y’Imana\tnatwe tura muhana ibihano bininiya cane"
  73,17,"Mwebwe nimwa hakana, mushobora gute kwikingira n’ivyago vy’umusi uzogira ibibondo kuba banaze imvi nk’abatama"
  73,18,"Amajuru azo satagurika kuri uwo musi, amasezerano yayo azo kurikizwa atagisivya"
  73,19,"Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu n’ubutumwa bw’Imana, rero uwushaka azo kwigirira inzira yiwe nziza ku Muremyi wiwe"
  73,20,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije yuko wewe uhagarara hafi y’ibice bibiri vy’ica gatatu c’ijoro, canke igice cayo n’uwundi mwanya ugahagarara kugice cica gatatu, na bamwe mu bantu muri kumwe nabo bagira nk’ibi hamwe na wewe, n’Imana niyo itegura neza ukugene uburebure bw’ijoro n’umutaga bungana, kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije yuko udashobora kugira ivyo, ikaba yarabagiriye ikigongwe kuri ivyo, rero ni musome ibiba yabaye kiborohereye kuri mwebwe mu majambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani, kuko irafise ubumenyi yuko bamwe muri mwebwe bazoba bakitswe n’amagara, abandi nabo bazoba bari mu rugendo ngaha kw’Isi barondera imigisha y’Imana, n’abandi nabo barwana mu nzira y’Imana, rero ni musome kubi boroheye muri ico gitabu gitagatifu, c’Imana hanyuma muhagarike amasengesho yanyu n’ugutanga imperezwa zanyu, hanyuma mubegurire Imana ikimanyu ciza, n’ineza iyariyo yose muzo yitanguza kubera imitima yanyu muzoyisanga ku Mana ari nziza cane, kandi ifise imigisha mininiya cane, kandi musabe ikigongwe ku Mana yanyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise imbabazi nyinshi cane n’impuhwe zihagije"
  74,1,Wewe wipfutse amahuzu
  74,2,Haguruka utuze abantu
  74,3,Uninahaze Umuremyi wawe
  74,4,Usukure n’impuzu zawe
  74,5,N’amabi yose ntuyiteho
  74,6,"Kandi\tntugire\tineza\tkubiremwa\tkugira\tngo\turonke\tumusesekara w’amaronko ngaha kw’isi"
  74,7,"Kubera Umuremyi wawe, wewe niwigumye gusa"
  74,8,Niha vuzwa inzamba y’umuhero w’isi
  74,9,Kuri uwo musi uzoba ari umusi uhambaye cane
  74,10,"Kubahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, uwo musi ntuzoba woroshe kuribo namba"
  74,11,Jewe n’undeke hamwe nuwo niremeye jewe nyene
  74,12,Ndamuhezagire aronke amatungo menshi
  74,13,N’ibibondo biboneka ahariho hose
  74,14,Ndamugirira ibintu vyiwe neza cane
  74,15,Hanyuma yizera yuko nzomwongereza
  74,16,Oya! Mu vy’ukuri yahora ahakana amajambo yacu meranda
  74,17,Rero nzo muhana n’ibihano bininiya cane
  74,18,Mu vy’ukuri yariyumviriye n’ugupima
  74,19,"Arahonywa, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,20,"Kandi yarahonejwe, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,21,Hanyuma yaritegereje
  74,22,Hanyuma arazinga mumaso yiwe kugeza naho haboneka iminkanyari
  74,23,Hanyuma ukuri aguha umugongo wiwe n’ukwishima cane
  74,24,"N’ukuvuga ati:- ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari uburozi bwabuwe"
  74,25,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari amajambo y’umuntu asanzwe
  74,26,Ubu vuba nzomuta mu muriro udahera
  74,27,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo muriro udahera
  74,28,Udasigaza nico usigaza
  74,29,Uwo muriro nuwu babura urukoba rimwe na rimwe
  74,30,Hejuru yuwo muriro udahera hariho abawucungera bashika kw’icumi n’icenda
  74,31,"Ntitwashizeho abacungera uwo muriro udahera atari abamarayika, kandi ntitwagize igitigiri cabo cumi n’icenda atari uko ari ikibazo kuri barya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri kugira ngo bashirwe n’abahawe ibitabu imbere yanyu, n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagumane ukwemera kwabo, kandi ntibagire amakenga bamwe bahawe igitabu imbere yanyu canke aba Isilamu n’abazoba bafise indwara mu mitima yabo hamwe n’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baze bavuge bati:- Imana yashatse kugira iki kuri kano karorero? Uku rero niko Imana ireka umuntu akazimira kuwo yishakiye n’ukurongora uwo yishakiye, kandi nta numwe afise ubumenyi bw’ukumenya ingabo z’Umuremyi wawe atariyo yonyene gusa, kandi ntivyari kuba atari ikimenyetso kubiremwa vyose"
  74,32,Sivyo none ? Ndarahiye k’ukwezi
  74,33,N’Ijoro rikeye
  74,34,No mugitondo hakeye
  74,35,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera n’umwe mungorane niniya zihambaye cane
  74,36,N’igabisho ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwushaka muri mwebwe n’atanguze kuja imbere canke aje inyuma
  74,38,"Umutima\tw’umwumwe\twese\tuzo\tkwugaranirwa\tmu\tmuriro\tudahera kubera ibikorwa bibi wakoze"
  74,39,Dukuye mwo abantu b’iburyo
  74,40,Abo bantu bazoba mu mirima babazanya
  74,41,Kubera abantu babi
  74,42,N’ikintu nyabaki cabatwaye mu muriro udahera
  74,43,"Bazo vuga bati:- ntitwari mu bantu bahora basenga"
  74,44,Kandi ntitwahora duha abakene ibifungugwa
  74,45,Kandi twahora twibira mu bicumuro hamwe n’abahora bibira
  74,46,Kandi twahora duhakana yuko ata musi w’uguciribwa imanza
  74,47,Kugeza n’aho dushikirwa n’urupfu
  74,48,Ntaco bizofasha uko gusaba kw’abasabira abaribo bose
  74,49,Mbega bafise iki ? Ntibitaho kuri rino tuza
  74,50,Nkuko umengo n’indogobwe zigenda ningoga na ningoga
  74,51,Ziruka nk’intare
  74,52,"Umwe wese muribo\tagomba yuko ahabwa impapuro zizoba zanditswe ko"
  74,53,Oya! kuri bo ntibatinya umuhero w’Isi
  74,54,"Oya ! Si uko, mu vy’ukuri ubwo n’ubwibutso"
  74,55,Rero uwushaka azokwibuka
  74,56,"Ntibazo kwibuka atari uko Imana yabishatse, kuko niyo ikwiwe gutinywa n’ukugira imbabazi"
  75,1,Ndarahiye k’umusi w’umuhero w’isi
  75,2,Kandi ndarahiye k’umutima widoga
  75,3,Yibaza umuntu yuko twebwe tutazo kwegeranya amagufa yiwe
  75,4,"Kubera iki, twebwe turashoboye kuringaniza amasonga y’intoke ziwe"
  75,5,Mugabo umuntu ashaka gusa guhakana ibiri imbere yiwe gusa
  75,6,Akabaza nk’agahemo uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi uzobera
  75,7,N’umusi ijisho ry’umuntu rizobona nk’umuravyo
  75,8,N’ukwezi mugihe kuzo fatwa
  75,9,N’Izuba hamwe n’Ukwezi bizo huzwa ariko gufatwa
  75,10,"Umuntu azo vuga kuri uwo musi ati:- ni uruhe ruhande rw’ukwirukira"
  75,11,Oya! Nta hantu hukwirukira
  75,12,Kuri uwo musi ingaruka ya vyose ni ku Muremyi wawe gusa
  75,13,"Kuri uwo musi umuntu azobwirwa kuvyo yagize aho hambere, hamwe nivyo yagize mu nyuma yaho"
  75,14,Ahubwo umuntu niwe cabona c’umutima wiwe
  75,15,Naho atanga ivyitwazo vyiwe vy’ububeshi
  75,16,Ntunyiganze ururimi rwawe mu kuru girira ivyihutirwa bimanuka
  75,17,Mu vy’ukuri ni kuri twebwe kuwegeranya n’ukuwigisha
  75,18,"Mugihe twebwe tugusomera, wewe n’ukurikize uko gusomwa kwavyo"
  75,19,Hanyuma ni hejuru yacu kubikwereka
  75,20,"Sivyo none, ahubwo mwebwe nimwe mukunda ubuzima bwaha kw’isi"
  75,21,N’ukureka ubuzima bwo mw’ijuru
  75,22,Amaso y’abandi kuri uwo musi azoba asayangana
  75,23,Araba Umuremyi wabo
  75,24,N’ayandi maso kuri uwo musi azo kwizinga
  75,25,Azomenya yuko azoshikirwa n’ivyago bivuna agatiri gongo
  75,26,Sivyo none! Uku mugira mugihe umutima uzoshika kumagufa y’ibitugu vyabo
  75,27,"Hazovurwa hati :- ni nde ashobora kuvura uyu murwayi"
  75,28,Nawe akamenya yuko ari umwanya w’urupfu
  75,29,Mugihe hazokurikizwa umurundi k’uwundi
  75,30,"Kuri uwo musi n’ugucungerwa gusa, n’ukujanwa k’Umuremyi wawe"
  75,31,Ntiyemeye canke ntiyasenze
  75,32,Ahubwo yarahakanye n’ugusubira inyuma
  75,33,Hanyuma yaragiye ku bantu biwe nawe yijanda jandira
  75,34,"Uramaze gushikirwa n’ibihano vy’Imana, mbega biramaze kugushikira"
  75,35,"Hanyuma\turamaze\tgushikirwa\tn’ibihano\tvy’Imana,\tmbega\tbiramaze kugushikira"
  75,36,Mbega wiyumvira yuko umuntu azorekwa gutya nyene agende akagirire
  75,37,Mbega ntiyari ima ry’intanga ryatewe
  75,38,"Hanyuma riba ikimanyu c’amaraso, hanyuma Imana ira murema nuku muringaniza ari umuntu akwiye"
  75,39,"Hanyuma imugira impande zibiri, z’ukuba umugabo n’umugore"
  75,40,"Mbega\tntiyari\tkuba\tuyo\tariwe\tnyene\tubushobozi\tbw’ukuzura abashengeye bose"
  76,1,Mu vy’ukuri ikiremwa muntu carahitiwe n’umwanya muremure w’imyaka myinshi kita raba ikintu na kimwe kivurwa kuri we
  76,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twaremye umuntu biturutse kumbuto y’ubuzima ivanzwe ni y’umugabo hamwe ni y’umugore, kugira ngo tumugirire ibibazo, kuri ivyo tumugira uwumva n’ukubona"
  76,3,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara murongoye mu nzira zose azoba arimwo aba uwushima canke uwuhakana
  76,4,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba teguriye abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, iminyororo hamwe n’imigozi y’umuriro ukaze cane"
  76,5,Mu vy’ukuri abantu beranda bazonywa ibinyobwa bivanzwe mwo n’akamoto kitiriwe Kafuri
  76,6,"Iyo\tKafuri\tn’umwonga\tuzonywa\tmwo\tabantu\tberanda\tb’Imana\tukazo shunguruka mwo amazi afise ishunguruka ryiza nkuko bipfuza"
  76,7,Abo bantu ni bamwe bakwijije ibikenewe vyabo n’ugutinya umusi w’ishari ryawo uzo kwiragira hose
  76,8,"Naba gaburira ibi fungurwa aboro hamwe n’impfuvyi hamwe n’imbohe, mugihe nabo ku bwabo bakunda ivyo bifungurwa"
  76,9,"Mu mitima yabo bavuga bati:- tuba risha ibi bifungurwa kugushaka impuhwe z’Imana gusa, kuko ntidushaka kuri mwebwe impembo iyariyo yose canke yuko mwodushimira"
  76,10,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe dutinya ku Muremyi wacu uwo musi w’ingorane n’uburuhe
  76,11,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tizoba\tkingira\tn’ishari\tryuwo\tmusi\tn’ukuba\thuza n’imigisha yayo hamwe n’akanya muneza ntangere"
  76,12,"Imana\tizo\tbaha\takaganuke\tk’imirima\tyo\tmw’ijuru\thamwe\tn’impuzu zihwahutse kubera ukwigumya kwabo"
  76,13,"Iyo mw’ijuru bazo kwegamira kunyegamo z’iteka, nti bazobona yo izuba rikaze cane , canke imbeho ikaze cane kuribo"
  76,14,"N’ibitutu\tvyayo\tbizoba\tbiri\thafi\tcane\tkuri\tbo,\thamwe\tn’ivyamwa vyegeranye kubindi bishunguruka bigerekeranye kubindi kugera hasi"
  76,15,Bazo cishirizwa ibikoresho vy’umwakaka hamwe n’ibikombe bibonerana
  76,16,N’ibirahuri vy’umwakaka vyujujwe kurugero rumwe rukwiye
  76,17,"Iyo\tmw’ijuru\tbazonyweshwa\tibinyobwa\tbivanzwe\tmwo\tn’ikirungo citiriwe Tangawizi"
  76,18,Urwo n’uruzi ruri mw’ijuru rwitiriwe Sal’sabila
  76,19,"Bazo kikuzwa n’imisore isharije, ubabonye womengo n’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu za sanzajwe"
  76,20,"Ubonye ibirimwo, uzoca ubona imigisha hamwe n’ubwami bw’Imana bunini cane"
  76,21,"Hejuru yabo barafise impuzu zihwahutse z’ibara ry’urwatsi rubisi, hamwe n’izindi zihwahutse ziremereye gatoyi, kandi bazokwambikwa ingori z’umwakaka, n’Umuremyi wabo azoba nywesha ibinyobwa vyiza cane"
  76,22,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo mpembo yanyu yibijanye n’ibikorwa vyanyu vyemewe
  76,23,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakumanuriye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ibice bice
  76,24,"Rero n’urindire intahe y’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntugamburukire umwe muribo mubagira ibicumuro canke uwuhakana Imana yiwe y’ukuri"
  76,25,Ni wibuke izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mu gitondo no ku mugoroba
  76,26,"Mw’ijoro naho uyunamire ushize umutwe wawe hasi, kandi uyi ninahaze mw’ijoro mumwanya muremure"
  76,27,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tbantu\tbikundira\tubuzima\tbwo\tngaha\tkw’Isi\tgusa, n’ugusiga inyuma yabo umusi ugoye cane kuribo"
  76,28,"Twebwe twabaremye n’ugushira mwo ubushobozi mubihimba vy’imibiri yabo, dushatse twoshobora kuzana abandi bantu atari bo bameze nkabo"
  76,29,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso, rero kuwushaka azofata inzira imushikana ku Muremyi wiwe"
  76,30,"Kandi ntimushobora gushaka icarico cose Imana itabishatse, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  76,31,"Yinjiza uwo yishakiye mu migisha yayo, naba hemukiye imitima yabo yarabateguriye ibihano bibabaza cane"
  77,1,Ndarahiye kumiyaga izanwa buhoro buhoro
  77,2,No kumiyaga ihinda kunguvu nyinshi cane
  77,3,"No kumiyaga igurura ibicu, ikabigurura nkuko Imana ibishaka"
  77,4,Iga tandukanisha kure na kure ivyo bicu
  77,5,Ndarahiye kuba Marayika bashikiriza ubutumwa bw’Imana ku ntumwa z’Imana
  77,6,Mugukura impamvu kanaka canke gutuza
  77,7,Mu vy’ukuri ibi mwemerewe ntankeka bizoshika
  77,8,Mugihe inyenyeri zizo hanagurwa imico yazo
  77,9,N’amajuru igihe azo manyagurika
  77,10,N’imisozi igihe izo vungagurika
  77,11,N’intumwa z’Imana igihe zizo kwegeranywa
  77,12,Ni k’umusi uwuhe bagenewe ico gihe
  77,13,N’umusi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,14,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,15,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,16,Mbega ntitwahoneje abantu ba kera burundu
  77,17,Hanyuma dukurikiza ko abandi bantu
  77,18,Uko niko tuzobagira abandi bazoba bari mumakosa
  77,19,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,20,Mbega ntitwabaremye mumazi ahoya hoya
  77,21,Hanyuma tuyashira ahantu haturuye
  77,22,Kugeza kukiringo kizwi
  77,23,"Natwe tugereranya umwanya w’ukuboneka kw’ikibondo, natwe ni beza mukugereranya"
  77,24,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,25,Mbega twebwe ntitwagize iy’Isi kugira ngo twegeranye abantu bose
  77,26,Mubiri bizima hamwe n’ivyapfuye
  77,27,"No\tmuriyo\tduhashira\tmwo\timisozi\tmire\tmire\titsimbataye\tneza\thasi n’ukubanywesha amazi meza y’umusarara"
  77,28,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,29,Ni mugende kuri vya bihano mwahora muhakana
  77,30,Ni mugende muri ca gitutu c’umuriro gifise impande zitatu
  77,31,"Ntikibapfuka\tico\tgitutu\tcanke\tntikibahengeshanya\tn’ukwaka\tkuwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  77,32,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tutanga\timishwarara\tyawo\tingana nk’amazu"
  77,33,Nkuko womengo n’ingamiya ifise ibara ry’umuhondo
  77,34,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,35,Uno musi n’umusi waho ata nakimwe bavuga
  77,36,Kandi ntibazo habwa uruhusha kugira ngo bisigure
  77,37,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,38,"Uwu\tn’umusi\tw’intahe\ty’ukuri,\ttwabegeranije\tmwese\thamwe n’ababayeho imbere yanyu"
  77,39,Ni mwaba mufise izindi ngeso ni muzigire hejuru yanje
  77,40,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,41,"Ntankeka\taba\tninahaza\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmu\tbitutu n’imyonga"
  77,42,N’ivyamwa bakunda
  77,43,"Ni mufungure kandi munywe n’akanya muneza ntangere, kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"
  77,44,Uku rero niko duhemba abagira ineza
  77,45,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,46,"Ni mufungure kandi mwinezereze gatoyi gusa, mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri abononyi"
  77,47,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,48,"Babwiwe bati :- ni mupfukame, ntibigera bapfukama namba"
  77,49,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,50,Mbega n’ibiganiro nyabaki inyuma yibi biganiro vy’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani bazo kwemera